Summary: Lstening to scanner, overheard a South West pilot describing green and white lights in cockpit. not from the ground
divs: Sighting DetailsListening to scanner. overheard SouthWest Airline pilot descibe 2 different colored lights iluminating the cockpit. Described it as a green light and a white light alternating back and forth. Wasn't comming from the ground (Negative on a hand held laser)Pilot could not identify the origin of the lights. Pilot used a word at the time to describe situation to the tower. Can't remember what is was but I looked it up the next day and it meant strange situation for an airline to be in. something to that effect. Reported incident to our local MUFON Dr. with no response. Can't remember his altitude but he said it appeared to be coming from the sky
